<br>
&quot;Oooh, this had better be good!&quot; he murmered. The crows, his companions, along with mice, and wolfs, were scattered through out the earth to collect its secerets and report back to him. And obviously Corniocopia and Prometheus had found out something worth while. He placed his hand in his chin, resting it there, his legs folding into the ever famous &quot;indian style&quot;. He raised his brows.<br>
